This module adopts the same governance shape as terraform-aws-vpc,
terraform-aws-iam, and terraform-aws-s3: unified Foundation Plan §15.2
tagging, the central reusable CI workflow in
devotica-labs/terraform-shared-config, and conftest policies from
devotica-labs/terraform-policies.

Defaults are aligned with fintech compliance requirements: annual key
rotation (CIS AWS Foundations 3.8, RBI cyber-security guidance on key
lifecycle), 30-day deletion window (AWS production recommendation),
symmetric encrypt/decrypt (SSE-KMS for S3/EBS/RDS/Logs).

Multi-region keys are opt-in for cross-region DR (RBI data-durability
mandate).

